6
00:00:37,140 --> 00:00:38,860
♪I'm roaming far and wide♪

7
00:00:39,220 --> 00:00:42,500
♪A twist of fate in desperate times♪

8
00:00:42,780 --> 00:00:46,020
♪A bond that outlives the dust of life♪

9
00:00:47,300 --> 00:00:50,700
