417
00:23:26,440 --> 00:23:27,490
But you have great eyes.

418
00:23:27,790 --> 00:23:28,460
Very clear.

419
00:23:31,030 --> 00:23:31,700
Miss,

420
00:23:32,000 --> 00:23:32,730
