533
00:28:10,680 --> 00:28:11,620
in my hands.

534
00:28:19,070 --> 00:28:19,770
Anyway, you passed.

535
00:28:19,880 --> 00:28:20,330
Take them.

536
00:28:21,680 --> 00:28:22,250
You

537
00:28:22,440 --> 00:28:23,330
barely pass.

538
00:28:23,920 --> 00:28:24,730
